src:
Hasil FP1 Moto2 Malaysia: Tetsuta Nagashima Asapi Brad Binder
01 Nov 2019, 09:50 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Pebalap ONEXOX TKKR SAG Team, Tetsuta Nagashima, sukses mencatatkan waktu tercepat dalam sesi latihan bebas pertama (FP1) Moto2 Malaysia di Sirkuit Sepang pada Jumat (1/11/2019).
Pebalap Jepang ini diikuti oleh pebalap Red Bull KTM Ajo, Brad Binder, di posisi kedua, dan pebalap Estrella Galicia 0,0 Marc VDS, Alex Marquez, di posisi ketiga.
Sementara itu posisi keempat dan kelima masing-masing ditempati oleh pebalap Dynavolt Intact GP, Thomas Luthi, dan pebalap Speed Up Racing, Jorge Navarro.
Berikut hasil FP1 Moto2 Malaysia 2019.
text:
Malaysian Moto2 FP1 Results: Tetsuta Nagashima Asapi Brad Binder
Nov 01 2019, 09:50 by Bola.net
Bola.net - ONEXOX TKKR SAG Team racer, Tetsuta Nagashima, successfully recorded the fastest time in the first free practice session (FP1) of Moto2 Malaysia at the Sepang Circuit on Friday (1/11/2019).
The Japanese rider was followed by Red Bull KTM Ajo rider Brad Binder in second place, and Estrella Galicia 0.0 Marc VDS, Alex Marquez, in third position.
Meanwhile the fourth and fifth positions were each occupied by Dynavolt Intact GP rider, Thomas Luthi, and Speed Up Racing rider, Jorge Navarro.
Following are the results of FP1 Moto2 Malaysia 2019.
